{"type": "article", "id": 3248, "title": "潜水艇卫浴收纳套件", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-04T08:08:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052329144f5cYOqIjoMUEeiA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t意大利家居品牌 Seletti 推出的这套多功能卫浴收纳套件，将潜水艇的造型运用于日常家居用品当中。整个“潜水艇”被分成 4 个模块，便于用户进行清洁。4 个模块相互之间依靠磁铁吸引，使之成为一艘完整的“潜水艇”，包括一个牙刷架、皂液器、棉棒收纳盒以及首饰盒子。黄、蓝、红、白 4 色可选，定价 71.5 美元，<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00GJ33DBK?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=wiredte-20\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232912w2eAaiSg9ZI3VLHr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232913jXFI0lW3T4QV7vdE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:11px;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:11px;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}